    "abstractNote": "The paper focuses on the first decades and centuries of Christian-Muslim relations, with emphasis on the Northern Mesopotamia. It also presents translations into Czech of two sources \u2013 the \u201cEdessene Apocalypse\u201d and short part of the \u201cZuqn\u012bn Chronicle\u201d. Using these historical texts as examples the author highlights both the apocalyptic mood in the society of the time and the issue of early conversions from Christianity to Islam.",
